Author: deeznutellaz
Text: Omg yesterday at uni I kept staring at this girl's waist and torso and I didn't want her to be creeper out so I stopped but I was SO fascinated by how skinny she was and was freaking out... Off topic but shit like that reminds me I'm NOT okay and I'm not 'uwu healthy asf I just wanna lead a healthier lifestyle' and I'm actually starving and have an ED...
